                            </ul>
                            <ul class="right">
                              <li>Manual temperature control</li>
                              <li>Telephone</li>
                              <li>Wi-Fi in your room</li>
                              <li>Minibar</li>
                              <li>Iron in room</li>
                              <li>RJ 45 outlet</li>
                              <li>Full kitchen</li>
                              <li>Microwave in room</li>
                              <li>Coffee/tea making facilities</li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="pane3{{ loop.index }}" class="tab-pane">
                          <div class="tab-packages-main">
                            <div class="massage-package">
                              <h2>MASSAGE PACKAGE</h2>
                              <div>Each apartment features a queen size bed in the bedroom a separate lounge with sofa bed and dining area fully equipped kitchen laundry bathroom and a private outdoor terrace with aundry bathroom and </div>
